data.title: Newton Women's Fate 8 Shoe - 2023
data.meta_description: Newton Women's Fate 8 Shoe is the ideal cushioned trainer for everyday and perfect for the new-to-Newton runner. Featuring a plush form-fitting upper and gender tuned to maximize both fit and performance.
data.text:
The Fate 8 is the ideal cushioned trainer for everyday and perfect for the new-to-Newton runner. Featuring a plush form-fitting upper and gender tuned to maximize both fit and performance, it will help you run healthier & happier for miles to come. And, our innovative sustainable construction uses recycled materials and Ecopureâ„¢ to increase biodegradability up to 75% to ensure your footprints disappear even faster in the future.

UPPER

Gender Optimized Fit - The new generation features substantial fit upgrades to keep you comfortable and at your best. Their gender tuning customizes the fit specifically to you, while their lining and lace configurations enhance security and eliminate potential friction and pressure points.

Plush 3D Engineered Mesh

Seamless, Breathable, Durable

HyLyte Cushioned Insole

SOLE TECHNOLOGY

Gender Tuned Action Reaction Technology - The magic powering Newton Running shoes is the revolutionary full foot Action/Reaction Technology system. The lugs on the sole compress and rebound as you move through each stride, creating a responsive, trampoline-like cushioning system that provides greater impact absorption, quicker bounce-back, and less energy loss than traditional foam core running shoes.

Gender Tuned XPS Diffusion Plate & Membrane

New Hytrel Infused Footbed

Newtonium Heel Cushioning
